description:
Rick Stroud talks Dan about the Tampa Bay Buccaneers. Rick explains to Dan how he broke the Antonio Brown story with the fake vaccination card. Ian Rapoport says that COVID sucks. Ian tells Dan about his interview with Urban Meyer.
